  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK394">
<l>uvappat talaikkūṭi yuḷḷap pirital</l>
<l> aṉaittē pulavar toḻil</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is the part of the learned to give joy to those whom they meet, and on leaving, to make them think (Oh! when shall we meet them again.)</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
